<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Spring on Kevin wang's blog</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/categories/spring/</link><description>Recent content in Spring on Kevin wang's blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 17:41:02 +0200</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://kevinwang930.github.io/categories/spring/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Spring Transaction Internals: Architecture, Lifecycle, and Nested Transaction Mechanics</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/transaction/</link><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 17:41:02 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/transaction/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Spring Transaction is one of the most critical modules in the Spring Framework. Whether using the declarative &lt;code&gt;@Transactional&lt;/code&gt; or the programmatic &lt;code&gt;TransactionTemplate&lt;/code&gt;, the underlying system is built on a highly abstract and elegantly designed transaction management infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post dissects the inner workings of Spring transactions across &lt;strong&gt;architectural design&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;core components&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;transaction execution lifecycle&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;nested transaction mechanics&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;transaction synchronizations&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;code&gt;afterCommit&lt;/code&gt; and related callbacks).&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Spring Cache internals</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/cache/</link><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 13:55:13 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/cache/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Spring Cache provides a lightweight abstraction over caching implementations and is driven by annotations such as &lt;code&gt;@Cacheable&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;@CachePut&lt;/code&gt;, and &lt;code&gt;@CacheEvict&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Spring kafka implementation</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/data/event/kafka/spring_kafka/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 13:47:04 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/data/event/kafka/spring_kafka/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This article introduces spring kafka Implementation&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Spring Expression Language</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/spel/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 21:09:34 +0700</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/spel/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Spring Expression Language (&amp;ldquo;SpEL for short&amp;rdquo;) is a powerful expression language that support querying and manipulating an object graph at runtime.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Spring Core Container</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/spring-core-container/</link><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:30:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/spring-core-container/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;本文介绍spring Core Container&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Spring Webflux</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/spring-webflux/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:43:22 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/spring-webflux/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;WebFlux is non-blocking, asynchronous web framework based on project Reactor.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Mybatis internals</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/mybatis/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 18:45:41 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/mybatis/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;本文介绍 Mybatis 以及 spring-mybatis 的架构与实现&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>spring-Logging</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/logging/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:46:28 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/logging/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;本文记录spring logging 的原理与配置&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Spring Security</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/security/</link><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:25:39 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/security/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;本文记录spring 安全相关的内容&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>spring aop 架构与实现</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/aop/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:44:12 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/aop/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;本文记录 spring aop 架构与实现&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Spring MVC</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/mvc/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:39:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/mvc/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This article describes Spring MVC&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Spring Boot internals</title><link>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/spring-boot/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 23:29:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kevinwang930.github.io/post/java/spring/spring-boot/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;本文介绍springBoot架构与实现&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>